- Create the new App

> rails _4.2.6_ new composer --database=postgresql --skip-test-unit --skip-bundle

- Open your Gemfile 

source 'https://rubygems.org'
source 'http://gems.github.com'

- Now run a bundle install to install the gem

Install postgres gem file
> gem install pg

. rails generate controller Welcome index

. add the following route to the routes.rb

	root 'welcome#index'

add the app to Github
. username: beimar.medina@outlook.com password: P@ss(0)d!
